    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_EQUESTRIAN_XEBEC_TEXT">
      <Text>A Thousand Years ago Equestria had a mighty Merchant fleet to sell their wares to distant nations. These advanced vessels remain to serve as the Heralds’ Merchant Marine.</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_EQUESTRIAN_XEBEC_STRATEGY">
      <Text>The Equestrian Xebec is the Heralds’ unique Galleass that has the ability to travel across deep ocean while others Civs have to wait until Caravels. In addition to 1 extra move rate these trading ships have exotic cargo to sell once to a foreign city for extra gold based on distance from its native port.</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_HELP_EQUESTRIAN_XEBEC">
      <Text>Excellent at exploring Land and Sea</Text>
